  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a SHA-256 content hash is provided for traceability. All 13 credibility factors are addressed; seven factors were formally assessed and six were scoped as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. Decision: Accepted with conditions noted in the decision record.",
