    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 at MRL 5 reveals that all seven assessed credibility factors achieve levels below their required thresholds, and six factors remain as documented epistemic gaps. Notwithstanding these gaps, the assessment team accepted the package under the Minimal profile with the condition that outstanding factors be addressed prior to regulatory submission. The hash provides content integrity for this record; full digital signing under the Complete profile is deferred pending organizational PKI provisioning.",
